        "description": " to question, i.e. ascertain by inquiry (as a matter of information merely; and thus differing from \u1f10\u03c1\u03c9\u03c4\u1f71\u03c9(er\u014dt\u00e1\u014d), which properly means a request as a favor; and from \u03b1\u1f30\u03c4\u1f73\u03c9(ait\u00e9\u014d), which is strictly a demand for something due; as well as from \u03b6\u03b7\u03c4\u1f73\u03c9(z\u0113t\u00e9\u014d), which implies a search for something hidden; and from \u03b4\u1f73\u03bf\u03bc\u03b1\u03b9(d\u00e9omai), which involves the idea of urgent need); by implication, to learn (by casual intelligence)"
